metadata.name: LAS FLORES CRECEN DE NOCHE
metadata.description: Glowing Records / CAF - Cosmovision 20 20 - No. 1 LAS FLORES CRECEN DE NOCHE (Flowers grow at night): is an intimate and solitary work, which represents the silent and dark processes where we usually hit rock bottom. It is cold, but necessary, it is slow, but important. Flowers represent our ideas, our brightest qualities, and how little they are visible in a materialistic and selfish world, emphasizing that we enjoy the best of ourselves out of the visibility of others, at night, in the dark. // February 1, 202 3 / MP4 / 1080 × 1080 ⨀
